{"tid":2373092,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"撇甩鄭衍峰即有新歡？馮盈盈密會西裝男歎意大利菜","createTime":"2021-01-20T07:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T11:20:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"492c0913247c4a211891a9e9740d0ff1d3dd9f46","tid":2373092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/V6f75LEY7jlI0ZaSa9nBsQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/5fdd77f0-5acc-11eb-a5de-c7e1f1955682\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FV6f75LEY7jlI0ZaSa9nBsQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2F5fdd77f0-5acc-11eb-a5de-c7e1f1955682&h=f9b420e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前港姐冠軍馮盈盈（FYY）最近成為新聞女王，認真多是非，前醫生男友鍾文浩今個月底結婚娶女友，而跟她傳緋聞的鄭衍峰因不滿不獲「正名」而與她吵大鑊，最終FYY棄兵，連朋友都做不成。<br />\n<br />\n不過年僅26歲，有樣有身材又轉數快的FYY怎會寂寞，有消息指她於上星期4密會留鬚西裝男，貌似一位事業型男士，２人於一間中環高級意大利餐廳食Lunch，而該間餐廳是城中有名的食府，擁有米芝蓮三星，午餐人均消費要$1,500，2人挑選角落位置坐下，貪地方夠隱蔽，有指大部分時間都是FYY說話，西裝男以笑容回應，FYY更不時使出電眼冧對方，兩人傾足2小時，為免被人影到，兩人前後腳離開，FYY果然醒目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UcbAjNNgrwYYiU644TSMPg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/b17eaf70-5acc-11eb-abde-a93e9f4e6ecd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUcbAjNNgrwYYiU644TSMPg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2Fb17eaf70-5acc-11eb-abde-a93e9f4e6ecd&h=e54492eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢回覆東網否認係新歡，表示：「只係普通朋友，我向佢請教投資意見，順便食飯啫，係討論完公事，先閒談咗幾句。只是爆料者無偷拍到前面，誤導了大家，而且同朋友食lunch係正常社交，限聚令只准兩人一枱，依家出去食飯都一定係撐枱腳啦，大家無需大驚小怪，見面食個飯，都要講到係新歡？其實有冇考慮過我朋友感受？我隨時拉低佢可發展對象嘅平均質素，影響到我朋友個market，佢又不是圈內人士，希望大家講我好喇，請不要再打擾到佢。」"},{"pid":"2efe9dbce93e71f99007bb088071afe7fc38e0a9","tid":2373092,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"畀咗幾多錢廣告東方炒緋聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469262d65708b5241845d248a0f87d5ace72e362","tid":2373092,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233af8ffeeb93f4c8df0dc78a0167bb3b59c4faf","tid":2373092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"469262d65708b5241845d248a0f87d5ace72e362","tid":2373092,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}